title: Status message that gives information about the feed operation and is received once per second. See Admin Port System Messages

ServerIP.title: IP address for least loaded Quote Server.

ServerPort.title: Port for least loaded Quote Server.

MaxSymbols.title: The maximum # of symbols that can be watched at any given time.

NumberOfSymbols.title: The # of symbols that are currently being watched.

ClientsConnected.title: The # of clients that are currently connected.

SecondsSinceLastUpdate.title: The # of seconds since the last update from the Quote server .

Reconnections.title: The # of times that IQFeed has reconnected.

AttemptedReconnections.title: The # of times that IQFeed has attempted to reconnect, but failed.

StartTime.title: The time that the connection (or reconnection) to IQFeed was made.

MarketTime.title: The current time of the market.

Status.title: Represents whether IQFeed is connected or not.

IQFeedVersion.title: Represents the version of IQFeed that is running.

LoginID.title: The Login ID that is currently logged in.

TotalKiloBytesReceived.title: Found in the "Internet Bandwidth" section of the IQConnection Manager. Formula: total bytes received / 1024.

KiloBytesPerSecReceived.title: Found in the "Internet Bandwidth" section of the IQConnection Manager. Formula: bytes received in the past second / 1024.

AvgKiloBytesPerSecRecv.title: Found in the "Internet Bandwidth" section of the IQConnection Manager. Formula: total KB's received / total seconds.

TotalKiloBytesSent.title: Found in the "Local Bandwidth" section of the IQConnection Manager. Formula: total bytes sent / 1024.

KiloBytesPerSecSent.title: Found in the "Local Bandwidth" section of the IQConnection Manager. Formula: bytes sent in the past second / 1024.

AvgKiloBytesPerSecSent.title: Found in the "Local Bandwidth" section of the IQConnection Manager. Formula: total KB's sent / total seconds
